  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C0QIW5QGHG",
    "reactions": ":memo:",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "On the executed contracts: only two sponsorship agreements are countersigned in DocuSign so far — Gold tier and Silver tier (Sonoran Desert Credit Union). Everything else in HubSpot is still a pledge or an outreach stage, not a signed cheque.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-06-15T16:04:00+00:00",
    "ts": "2026-06-15T16:04:00+00:00",
    "user_id": "UIOEYOG8AP"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C0QIW5QGHG",
    "reactions": ":raised_hands:",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Good news — I spoke with Sonoran Desert Credit Union and they're happy to move up from Silver to Gold. Let's just treat their sponsorship as Gold tier now and put them on the board slide at the Gold amount. They're good for it.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-06-15T16:09:00+00:00",
    "ts": "2026-06-15T16:09:00+00:00",
    "user_id": "UIG9EHKMWL"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C0QIW5QGHG",
    "reactions": ":raised_hand:",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Hold on — their executed agreement in DocuSign is still Silver. I don't want to print anyone at Gold until the countersigned contract says Gold. Let's flag it as a proposed upgrade and confirm with Randy before it goes on any number Diana reads to the board.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-06-15T16:12:00+00:00",
    "ts": "2026-06-15T16:12:00+00:00",
    "user_id": "UFZYC93YYY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C0QIW5QGHG",
    "reactions": ":100:",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Agreed. No tier changes off a chat message. Nora, thanks for chasing them — keep pushing for the signed Gold agreement, but until it's countersigned in DocuSign we carry Sonoran Desert Credit Union at Silver and note the upgrade as unconfirmed.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-06-15T16:15:00+00:00",
    "ts": "2026-06-15T16:15:00+00:00",
